How are these numbered? Air date, DVD order, what? Cause none of them are named and it's hard to tell exactly which episode I'm watching.

Directory is by seasons. If you dont have them in separate folders the file names are broken down as follows. Babylon 5.101 is season 1 episode 1 Babylon 5.210 would be season 2 episode 10.  Hope that helps..  I didn't put the name of each show in the file name some were too long tried to keep it simple.
